design:
Estimated effort: 2-3 hours

Migrate the following types to use InferSelectModel:
- Transaction
- Category
- Budget
- Income
- Recurring
- Savings
- SavingsGoal
- Contribution
- User

Example pattern:
```typescript
import type { InferSelectModel } from 'drizzle-orm';
import { transaction, category, budget, income } from '$lib/server/db/schema';

export type Transaction = InferSelectModel<typeof transaction> & {
  category: Category | null;
  user: User;
};

export type Category = InferSelectModel<typeof category>;
export type Budget = InferSelectModel<typeof budget> & {
  category: Category | null;
  user: User;
};
export type Income = InferSelectModel<typeof income>;
```

Benefits:
- Types automatically sync with schema changes
- Reduced maintenance burden
- Prevents type drift
- Single source of truth
